title: Oats, Commercial Stocks for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1873-1885 (2)--Original Data, 1884-1889 (3)--Original, 1888-1927 (4)--Original, 1926-1954. Data Refeer To Domestic Oats Only -- In Store In Public And Private Elevators, In 39 Markets, And Oats Afloat In Vessels Or Barges In Harbors Of Lakes And Seaboard Ports, On The Saturday Nearest The First Of The Month. Source: Data For 1927-June 1941: U.S. Department Of Agriculture, Agricultural Statistics, Issues Of 1937 (P. 57), 1938 (P. 62), 1940 (P. 69), 1942 (P. 77); Data For July 1941-1954: U.S. Department Of Commerce, Survey Of Current Business, Statistical Supplements Of 1942, 1947, 1949, 1951, 1953, And Monthly Issues Thereafter

This NBER data series m05084d appears on the NBER website in Chapter 5 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter05.html.
